{"tid":1417790,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日發夢有行過金鐘銅鑼灣既前線同我入泥！！！","createTime":"2019-08-05T17:11:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T17:18:18.000Z","uid":170218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"259523b0c6f3455b0db87d71b4648d060b38d3de","tid":1417790,"uid":170218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:11:16.000Z","msg":"利申借AC 前線靚絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於最近大家都玩香城Online瘋狂轉場<br />\n根本上瘋狂轉場都唔係玩緊popo 而係玩緊自己友<br />\n大家都拎住好重裝備同埋物資行咗幾萬步 都唔知自己做過啲咩 但係就攰到仆街<br />\n<br />\n所以我有個建議<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不如大家開個前線Tg group</span></strong></span><br />\n因為而家根本上好難分到邊個係咪前線<br />\n亦都好多人想帶風向<br />\n你唔會知邊個係唔係鬼<br />\n我唔係想分化和理非 但係呢兩日都試過比和理非帶住行 但結果真係唔係好work<br />\n<br />\n所以我覺得有咩可以喺Tg到溝通<br />\n大家有咩提議係個group到講"},{"pid":"0856ee524255fb21fe9ec83a5d743bc2165e9399","tid":1417790,"uid":170218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:13:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a6023e5692453de8100b5c8cc91b117683c99036","tid":1417790,"uid":170218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:13:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d782049a11e5d48a508b38d59acb005b141e2b34","tid":1417790,"uid":170218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:13:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"075cc62fe3924f317798f79cbb1510b9bb10fa96","tid":1417790,"uid":170218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:13:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"91181ef068bbb1244a8a615038aa43c63155c4f1","tid":1417790,"uid":170218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:14:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c0d60236883af21857f585e1aa8757c29e7d31a","tid":1417790,"uid":170218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:14:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"659ddc213c636cb539d710ec7e45106595809e12","tid":1417790,"uid":170218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"